name: ClearSkies
0:
”Alexa, ask Clear Skies for the air quality of New York.”
”What is the pollution of San Francisco?”
”What means moderate?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: clear skies
des:
The current air quality index (AQI) can be obtained for different cities.

The meaning for various air pollution levels like „moderate“ or „unhealthy“ can be retrieved also.


Data provided by World Air Quality Index Project.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
